## Next Steps

* The RPC will continue transitioning its production database toward GitHub, with the goal of eventually making collaborative final reviews in GitHub the default option.
* Mark Nottingham will continue to refine the `IETF LLM` and `IETF Skill` tools.
* The community and leadership will continue discussions on establishing formal moderation guidelines for automated agents on IETF mailing lists and GitHub repositories.